column5: Hi there can anyone help with info on a frabil ice cruiser 300, does it come with seats, price , thanks Blizz
Only thing I could find on another forum is that is does not come with seats, that's why it's lighter than some others.

Thanks fisherman for yor time, I  tried their web site but could not come up with anything, I have many pics with a frozen moustache and eyelashes and yes call me a wimp but at -47 windchills blocking the wind would be a little more comfortable.
